{"tid":1028452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夢想vs金錢","createTime":"2019-02-19T13:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T06:08:50.000Z","uid":49836,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b474222ee9f05ed675237b0dfe74126bae6cfc01","tid":1028452,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"認真討論<br />\n假設你有個夢想想實現好耐 或者你已經係追逐夢想既過程中(不論個夢想or目標幾偉大幾微小)<br />\n<br />\n如果有日話你知 你可以得到一筆錢(金額任你開) 但代價係永遠放棄你一直追逐緊既夢想 你地會點揀？<br />\n<br />\n立場無分對錯 亦唔係想討論個別夢想需要龐大資金實現 只係好想知大家如何看待夢想既價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\nPs 如果你放棄筆錢 唔代表你一定可以實現到你 有可能到你死個刻 筆錢又攞唔到 夢想又實現唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 揀要夢想 做人無夢想同條咸魚有咩分別 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夢想？不了 錢金係我存在既意義"},{"pid":"19598993926001cf67c061bafd69337b635416b2","tid":1028452,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:24:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610ad0a65cbe65242643913ad1c15e166f5710f8","tid":1028452,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9dfaeb6f9e0e4efce49d5010839a0deb993d09","tid":1028452,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4aa046fc733c37fe9fe6b92a4cb18d36628b9b7","tid":1028452,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c96ec6c59cee1b798ce0aab404754a22ead2448","tid":1028452,"uid":179680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"我夢想需要筆錢去實現"},{"pid":"a0975f1ff0fc3ebfd4ad68c0c1c400125